name: Vince the Videotape Doll
description:
Vince the Videotape doll.  He is 8" tall and soft and plush.

He was the created with the help of 143 backers on Kickstarter!

name: LIMITED Zombie Bacon
description:
Zombie Bacon is my Comic Con exclusive doll for 2013.  Only 1000 were made and sold at San Diego Comic Con.  Once these are gone, that is it.

Zombie Bacon is 10" tall

name: LIMITED Aisu the Ice Pop Doll - JUST HAVE ONE!
description: Aisu is a Cherry Ice Pop. He is 8" tall and soft and plush. He is a Limited Edition of 100 pieces. Each one has a hand drawn numbered tag. All proceeds from the sale of Aisu will be going to support Animal Rescue in Japan after the earthquake and tsunami. For more information on donating to this cause - Donations

name: Mr Toast Doll
description: This is the classic 7" Mr Toast doll. Just about the size of an actual piece of toast. Ready to come and be your new best friend. To enjoy his adventures, check out our website - The World of Mr Toast

name: Joe the Egg Doll
description: Mr Toast's best friend is Joe the Egg.  Here is is all happy and plump.  6" tall.

name: Shaky Bacon doll
description: To know him is to love him.  Shaky Bacon in doll form, 10" tall.

name: Clem Lemon Doll
description: Clem is one of Mr Toast's neighbors.  Only one tooth but a goofy good friend.  He is 9" tall.

name: Set of 4 Dolls
description: Get the main characters all at once.  Mr Toast (7"), Joe the Egg (6"), Shaky Bacon (10") and Clem Lemon (9")

name: Drunken Carrot Doll
description: He is orange and he has a problem.  Drunken Carrot is 10" tall

name: Lil' Leif Doll
description: This is Lil' Leif the Leaf.  Smallest of all our dolls, this little guy is about 6" tall.

name: Miles the Ice Pop Doll
description: Miles is a Lime Ice Pop.  He is 8" tall and soft and plush.

name: Sophie the Ice Pop Doll
description: Sophie is a Pink Lemonade Ice Pop.  8" tall and and Mr Toast's newest sweet friend.

name: Mega Mr Toast Doll
description: This is 11" of Mr Toast goodness.  Much bigger and better then the standard Mr Toast doll.

name: Mini Mr Toast w/ Clip
description: This is the smallest Mr Toast at only 4". He has a plastic clip so you can hang him around.

name: Mega Clem Lemon
description: If you liked the regular Clem Lemon, you will love this Mega Clem Lemon.  13" tall and 6" around, he is almost the size of a football and just as much fun.  Soft and plush.

name: Cornelius Candy Corn Doll
description: Cornelius Candy Corn doll - 9" tall

name: Vampire Candy Corn Doll
description: A little scary and a little fun.  9" tall

name: Shaky Bacon Resin handpainted
description: This is a handpainted resin figure of Shaky Bacon.  Sculpted by Pretty in Plastic and painted by Dan Goodsell.  5" tall. Limited Edition of 45 pieces.

name: Shaky Bacon Resin figure Unpainted
description:
This is a resin figure of Shaky Bacon.  Sculpted by Pretty in Plastic and painted by Dan Goodsell.  5" tall. 

This is an unpainted off white version.  Ready to be customized.

name: Mr Toast Button
description:
Pick from these four 1.25" buttons.  Choose Mr Toast Fan Club, I Heart Mr Toast, Best Friends or To the Rescue.

Made by Badge Bomb!

name: Mr Toast's Pals Button
description:
Pick from these four 1.25" buttons. Choose Shaky Bacon, Dancin' Fool, Pals or Nerdy.

Made by Badge Bomb!

name: Even More Mr Toast buttons
description:
Pick from these four 1.25" buttons. Choose Mope the Onion, Lemon Ed (Blah Blah Blah), Space Duck, Sr Cork and Glue Guy (Crafty)

Made by Badge Bomb!

name: Fight Evil Button
description: This is a fun little button I did for the 2013 SD Comic Con.  1.25" around with pinback

name: Mr Toast Stickers
description:
Each sticker is 3.5"x3.5".  Professionally printed.  But these are indoor stickers, not for cars or outdoor use (they wont hold up).

Choose from 9 designs.

name: Mr Toast Necklace
description: Mr Toast Necklace -  1.25" charm on 18" stainless steel chain.

name: Shaky Bacon Necklace
description: Shaky Bacon Necklace -  1.25" charm on 18" stainless steel chain.

name: Joe the Egg Necklace
description: Joe the Egg Necklace -  1" charm on 18" stainless steel chain.

name: Mr Toast Womens Shirt Small SALE!!!
description: This is an Mr Toast Womens T-Shirt. Teal shirt with a color heat transfer decal. Shirt is a Babydoll - ONLY SIZE IS SMALL!

name: Mr Toast & Buddies Wallet - NEW
description:
Mr Toast Wallet features images of Mr Toast and all his buddies.  Wallet background is light yellow with orange stitching.  Super shiny and durable thick vinyl outside with our signature crosshatch vinyl on the inside. There's is a large pocket for your cash and 4 pockets for your ID and credit cards.

Size is 3.75 x 4.25 inches closed.

Made by Tinymeat

name: Night Music - Mr Toast Comics #2
description: This is the second issue of Mr Toast Comics.  28 pages + cover - contains the 28 page story Night Music, written by Dan Goodsell and drawn by Todd Webb.  Book is full color and 6"x 7 3/4".

name: Shaky's Vacation - Mr Toast Comics #3
description: This is the third issue of Mr Toast Comics.  28 pages + cover - contains the 28 page story SHAKY's VACATION, written by Dan Goodsell and drawn by Todd Webb.  Book is full color and 6"x 7 3/4".

name: Ninja School - Mr Toast Comics #4
description: This is the fourth issue of Mr Toast Comics.  32 pages + cover - contains the 32 page story NINJA SCHOOL, written by Dan Goodsell and drawn by Todd Webb.  Book is full color and 6"x 7 3/4".

name: Subterra - Mr Toast Comics #5
description: This is the fifth issue of Mr Toast Comics.  28 pages + cover - contains the 28 page story Subterra: the World Below, written by Dan Goodsell and drawn by Todd Webb.  Book is full color and 6"x 7 3/4".

name: Little Lost Ghost - Mr Toast Comics #6
description: This is the sixth issue of Mr Toast Comics.  28 pages + cover - contains the 28 page story Little Lost Ghost, written by Dan Goodsell and drawn by Todd Webb.  Book is full color and 6"x 7 3/4".

name: Superheroes Comic
description:
The latest Mr Toast comic from 2010.  24 pages full color of Mr Toast and all his pals as Superheroes.  6x7".

Comic can be signed and personalized if you want.

name: Mr Toast Promo Comic
description: This is the promo comic "Welcome to the World of Mr Toast".  8 pages + cover - a fun little introduction to Mr Toast.  Book is full color and 6"x 7 3/4".

name: Kaleidoscope Book
description:
Hardback book - 6x7" - 2009 - 64 Pages of comics, photos and Mr Toast goodness

Book can be signed and personalized if you want.

name: Travelin' Color Ink Book
description: This is a 60 page coloring book.  Shows Mr Toast and his friends traveling all over the US and the World.  8.5x11" - black and white interior with Color Cover.  Produced by Color Ink Book.

name: Candied Bacon #1
description: This is a resin figure of Shaky Bacon.  Sculpted by Pretty in Plastic - These are done in clear resin with glitter inside.  5" tall. Your choice of Purple, Watermelon or Deep Blue!

name: Candied Bacon #2
description: This is a resin figure of Shaky Bacon.  Sculpted by Pretty in Plastic - These are done in clear resin with glitter inside.  5" tall. Your choice of Yellowish Light Green, Deep Forest Green and Red!

name: Candied Bacon #3
description: This is a resin figure of Shaky Bacon.  Sculpted by Pretty in Plastic - These are done in clear resin with glitter inside but in multiple layers of color.  5" tall. Your choice of Yellow/Purple/Blue Swirl, Turquoise/Green and Purple/Blue.

name: Candied Bacon #4
description: This is a resin figure of Shaky Bacon.  Sculpted by Pretty in Plastic - These are done in opaque resin so they are not clear.  5" tall. Your choice of Light Blue with glitter, Red and Gold.

name: Monster Cereal Print
description: This is a print of Mr Toast & Friends as the GM Monster cereal characters.  Mr Toast as Frankenberry, Joe as Boo Berry and Shaky Bacon as Count Chocula.  Print is 9x12" and signed and numbered.  Edition of 200.

name: Mr Toast TRON Print - on SALE
description:
This is a limited edition Tron Mr Toast Print.  This Digital Print is 11x14" and ready to frame.  Done for the Crazy for Cult 2010 Show at Gallery 1988.  Edition of 100, prints are signed and numbered.

LIMITED SUPPLY

name: Dance Party Print
description:
This is a limited edition Mr Toast DANCE PARTY Print.  This Digital Print is 11x14" and ready to frame.  Done for the Japan LA 2010 Mr Toast Party.  Edition of 250, prints are signed and numbered.

LIMITED SUPPLY

name: Mega Vampire Toast
description: This deluxe 11" Mega Vampire Toast, has a satin red and black cape and the fangs to match.

name: LIMITED Midnight Super Toast
description: This is the Midnight Edition of Super Toast.  Has a blue mask and cape.  Only 200 made.  Each comes with a handmade tag and numbered.

name: LIMITED Monster Toast Doll
description:
This is the very limited 7" Monster Toast Doll.  Only 100 made, each with a hand drawn and numbered tag.  Created for a Monster Plush Show at Gallery 1988 in 2008.

Limited Supply

name: LIMITED Super Toast doll
description: This Super Hero version of Mr Toast was an exclusive for the 2012 San Diego Comic Con.  7" tall and limited to only 1000 pieces.

name: LIMITED Frankentoast Doll
description: This monstrous version of Mr Toast was an exclusive for the 2011 San Diego Comic Con.  7" tall and limited to only 100 pieces.

name: LIMITED Devil Bacon Doll
description:
Devil Bacon was my Comic Con exclusive doll for 2010.  Only 1000 were made and sold at San Diego and NY Comic Con.  I found a few that got left home from the show.  When these are gone, that is it.

Devil Bacon is 10" tall

name: LIMITED Celeste the Ice Pop Doll
description:
Celeste is the Orange Ice Pop.  She is 8" tall and soft and plush.

Limited Edition of 100 pieces released at DesignerCon 2011.  Each one has a hand drawn numbered tag.

This is the final Limited Ice Pop, the other 2 Limited Ice Pops Mondo and Aisu are Sold Out.

name: LIMITED Mondo the Ice Pop Doll
description:
Mondo is a Grape Ice Pop.  He is 8" tall and soft and plush.

Limited Edition of 100 pieces for my art show at Monkeyhouse Toys in December 2010.  Each one has a hand drawn numbered tag.

name: Mr Toast Wallet - Back in Stock
description:
Mr Toast Wallet features images on both the inside and out.  Super shiny and durable thick vinyl outside with our signature crosshatch vinyl on the inside. There's is a large pocket for your cash and 4 pockets for your ID and credit cards.

Size is 3.75 x 4.25 inches closed.

Made by Tinymeat
